OL,3,CTrial date set for man charged after
OL,4,Cpedestrians hit by car in Derby
OL,6,FA man accused of dangerous driving
OL,7,Fafter seven people were injured when a
OL,8,Fcar hit pedestrians in Derby, will
OL,9,Fface trial later this year.
OL,11,F36-year-old Sandhu Ponnachan, of
OL,12,FChariot Close in Alvaston is charged
OL,13,Fwith six counts of causing grievous
OL,14,Fbodily harm with intent, one count of
OL,15,Fattempted grievous bodily harm, one
OL,16,Fcount of dangerous driving and one
OL,17,Fcount of possession of a bladed
OL,18,Farticle.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
