OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1777536371
OL,3,CTrial date set for man charged after
OL,4,Cpedestrians hit by car in Derby
OL,6,FPonnachan was not asked to enter any
OL,7,Fpleas at Derby Crown Court and was
OL,8,Fremanded in custody until a further
OL,9,Fhearing in July.
OL,11,FHe appeared in court by videolink to
OL,12,FHMP Manchester dressed in a grey
OL,13,Fsweater and jogging bottoms, and took
OL,14,Fnotes at several points during the 20-
OL,15,Fminute hearing.
OL,17,FIt's after four men and three women,
OL,18,Faged between 36 and 52, were hit by a
OL,19,Fblack Suzuki Swift on the evening of
OL,20,FMarch 28.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1777536371
OL,3,CTrial date set for man charged after
OL,4,Cpedestrians hit by car in Derby
OL,6,FAdjourning the case after submissions
OL,7,Ffrom prosecution counsel Hugh Davies
OL,8,FKC and defence barrister Julia King,
OL,9,FJudge Shaun Smith KC set Ponnachan's
OL,10,Ftrial date for September 28, with a
OL,11,Ftwo-week time estimate.
OL,13,FThe judge also ordered that Ponnachan,
OL,14,Fwho is originally from India, be
OL,15,Fassisted by a Malayalam interpreter at
OL,16,Ffuture hearings.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
