FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1777536371
OL,3,CTrial date set for man charged after
OL,4,Cpedestrians hit by car in Derby
OL,6,FJudge Smith told Ponnachan: "You are
OL,7,Fgoing to be remanded in custody. We
OL,8,Fare going to be back here on the 10th
OL,9,Fof July and we will see where we are
OL,10,Fgoing with this case."
OL,12,FDuring the hearing, Judge Smith also
OL,13,Fgave permission for witnesses at the
OL,14,Ftrial to give evidence from behind
OL,15,Fscreens or through pre-recorded
OL,16,Finterviews.
